      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, representing a sophisticated balance of performance and value. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic excellence. A premier choice for the driver seeking a dependable and refined pre-owned asset, this vehicle stands as a testament to quality craftsmanship.",
